Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我过来 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个炼狱先生 是柱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他长什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他的发色很显眼 气味我也记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,走近了就能认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
